2012-07-20  Ingo Renner  <ingo.renner@dkd.de>

	* Release of v2.2.0

	!! Renamed tx_solr_FacetRenderer::getFacet() to getFacetProperties()

	! Added method getFacetInternalType() in interface tx_solr_FacetRenderer
	! Renamed tx_solr_facet_Facet::getOptions() to getOptionsRaw()
	! Renamed tx_solr_Search::getFacetRangeOptions() to getFacetRangeOptions()
	! API cleanup
		* Changed tx_solr_pluginbase_PluginBase::performAction() to be abstract
		* Added missing abstract tx_solr_pluginbase_PluginBase::render()
	! Removed the default language filter
		* It is advised to have a separate core/index for each language due to different stemming per language
		* Fixes the issue that records indexed for all languages (-1) could not be found

	* Updated SolrPhpClient to r65
	* Updated jQuery to 1.7.2
	* Updated jQuery UI to 1.8.21

	* Fixed bug #35679:Index queue broken by new indexing priority feature, credits Michiel Roos
	* Changed tx_solr_pluginbase_PluginBase to execute postRender() also after renderError()
	* Added feature #35544: Configurable query parameter
	* Fixed bug #35665: An empty search disables the rendering of any plugin output, credits Stefan Sprenger
	* Added tx_solr_facet_FacetOption::isSelectedInFacet()
	* Fixed an issue with the selected state of facet options introduced with #35588, credits Stefan Galinksi
	* Added the tagetPage ID property to the TypoScript constants
	* Added the query GET parameter to constants
	* Added feature #36202: Add option to set domains to be searched, credits Stefan Sprenger
	* Removed title field from result highlighting fields
	* Added OpenSearch support
	* Fixed broken show results of empty query, credits Stefan Galinski
	* Fixed bug #35996: Page Indexer always stores absolute url
	* Fixed bug #35727: Configurable query parameter feature causes bug with the suggestion link
	* Added feature #34652: Add option search.faceting.keepAllFacetsOnSelection, credits Cornel Boppart
	* Changed EXT:news Index Queue configuration to index tags into separate field, using keywords field for keywords
	* Changed SOLR_RELATION to resolve labels for relations correctly even with intermediate tables, credits Steffen Ritter
	* Added a generic language schema without stemming for languages we do not have a schema for
	* Fixed bug #36623: Index Queue initialization crashes with erronous mount page
	* Change tx_solr_ConnectionManager::getConfiguredSolrConnections(): extract getConfiguredSolrConnectionByRootPage()
	* Added tx_solr_Site::getRootPage()
	* Added feature #36668: Allow Solr connection initialization per site
	* Change the page browser content object initialization to be switchable from USER_INT to USER, credits Dimitri Ebert
	* Fixed an issue where a relative URL could be detected as TypoScript path in LINK viewhelper
	* Added a button in the admin module to remove all documents of a selected site
	* Fixed a bug where creating a page translation did not trigger re-indexing of the page
	* Fixed a bug where hiding a page translation did not trigger garbage collection of the page
	* Fixed bug #36329: Opensearch does not provide L parameter
	* Added feature #36486: Initialize Solr connections via CLI
	* Added support for scheduler progress in TYPO3 6.0
	* Fixed issue #33464: Improve responsiveness of Garbage Collector when deleting or hiding pages or records
	* Added an option to allow setting results per page in the pi_results flexform
	* Added a configuration option to set the default sort order per sort option
	* Added a parameter for ATagParams to the link viewhelper, credits Andre Westbunk
	* Added a TypoScript option to control loading of Javascript files
	* Added a TypoScript option to set a fixed direction for sorting options
	* Added marker ###FACETING.active### to detect if any facet option has been selected
	* Added support for plugin commands returning array and objects for rendering in their template subparts
	* Changed the results per page switch to be a command on its own
	* Fixed bug #34558: Wrong processing of plugin.tx_solr.search.query.filter stdWrap in pi_search, credits Jochem de Groot
	* Added the implementation to make Javascript load at the end of a page
	* Added class tx_solr_facet_Facet to handle facets
	* Added implementation for tx_solr_facet_Facet->getSelectedOptions()
	* Added implementation for facet requirements evaluation
	* Added feature #34187: Conditional Facets
	* Added sorting default order to the sorting template properties, credits Michel Tremblay
	* Added dutch translation for backend labels, credits Rik Willems
	* Added tx_solr_Search::getFacetQueryOptions()
	* Changed constructor of facet renderers to use a facet object instead of a facet name
	* Changed tx_solr_facet_NumericRangeFacetRenderer to use tx_solr_facet_Facet through tx_solr_facet_AbstractFacetRenderer
	* Changed tx_solr_facet_Facet::getOptionsCount() to take into account the facet internal type
	* Added support for facet queries
	* Extracted all query link building methods to tx_solr_query_LinkBuilder
	* Moved query GET parameter configuration handling from plugin base to query link builder
	* Extracted all facet option query link building methods from tx_solr_facet_FacetOption to tx_solr_facet_LinkBuilder
	* Added a wrapping div to the no results subpart
	* Added marker FACETING.search_has_results
	* Fixed some performance issue in the template engine
	* Fixed handling of facet queries with no results
	* Fixed a memory leak in the Index Queue when indexing pages and config.sys_language_mode is not set
	* Extracted spellchecker into a separate class
	* Moved spell checking suggestions from the spell checking form modifier to the spell checker
	* Changed the no-results command to use the spell checker
	* Fixed the spell checker to use the current page id for URL/link generation
	* Added tx_solr_Spellchecker->isIncorrectlySpelled()
	* Refactored rendering of plugin commands
	* Changed the results command to use the search's query
	* Added tx_solr_pi_results_ResultsCommand->setSearch()
	* Added tx_solr_Query->getKeywordsCleaned()
	* Added feature to search using the spell checker suggestions when no results were found for the original query
	* Added option tx_solr.search.spellchecking.searchUsingSpellCheckerSuggestion
	* Added support for keepAllOptionsOnSelection with facet queries
	* Added API methods to the Index Queue to initialize specific indexing configurations only
	* Added a field in the backend module to select which Index Queue indexing configurations to initialize
	* Fixed handling of Javascript loading through the Javascript Manager
	* Added more information to the plugin backend summary in the page module view
	* Improved distinction between action areas in the backend module
	* Change url(en|de)code function calls to their raw equivalents, credits Stefan Galinksi
	* Fixed bug #37362: incomplete url for results per page switch
	* Fixed bug #37960: Missing htmlspecialchars for generated urls, credits Stefan Galinksi
	* Added feature #37723: Conditional Facets - More flexibility, credits Stefan Galinksi
	* Added feature #37845: Allow manual sorting of the facet options, credits Stefan Galinksi
	* Fixed a crash in the reports module for the case when a site has no TypoScript template
	* Fixed issue #37107: PHP Warning: Outdated Ext.Direct API inclusion, credits Stefan Galinksi
	* Fixed bug #38290: Empty typoscript for facet leads to fatal error when rendering through facet view helper
	* Fixed issue #38704: tomcat autostart script not LSB (Linux Standards Base)-compliant, credits Dirk Wenzel
	* Fixed an issues resulting in T_PAAMAYIM_NEKUDOTAYIM when running on PHP 5.2
	* Added an option to configure the type field used when grouping by type (markResultTypeBoundaries)
	* Fixed an issue with initializeWithEmptyQuery not issueing the empty query
	* Added feature #39080: Add ping time in status report
	* Changed garbage collection handling, some simplification with cleaning the index
	* Fixed issue #39037: Recordmonitor should respect additionalWhereClause setting in indexing queue, credits Jigal van Hemert

